},{"pid":"b5a91071b3cbfe1de752ab81218fcb50b0e83c46","tid":1422523,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"係時候食住個勢，比勇武收割光環!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422454</a>"},{"pid":"d5913a1d59c70e33791cd0d084148de3b47a4bb2","tid":1422523,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6f2111d5b9dbb332d504eb6292dc1dd066d85c56","tid":1422523,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baa483e9976e640e187e8f21db5c38839c810f4","tid":1422523,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"一齊關心林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850b511a1952f5d7347e669ede3510ffda9969c7","tid":1422523,"uid":261343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"偏執型人格障礙（paranoid personality disorder），又稱為妄想型人格障礙，特徵是極度敏感，對侮辱和傷害耿耿於懷；<span style=\"color: red;\">思考、行為刻板固執，心胸狹窄</span>；愛嫉妒，對別人的成就感到緊張不安；不能和家人和睦相處，<span style=\"color: red;\">與朋友、同事的關係也比較緊張，引來別人敬而遠之；自命不凡</span>，對自己的能力過於高估，同時又很自卑；對別人要求過高，又不信任別人，是一種同時集自卑和自大於一身的人格障礙。<br />\n<br />\n偏執型人格的人<span style=\"color: red;\">不願意服輸，明明知道是自己不對，也要千方百計地為自己辯護，理屈詞窮時，哪怕用詭辯的方式也要證明自己是對的。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.tvbs.com.tw/amp/ttalk/life/3898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Famp%2Fttalk%2Flife%2F3898&d=Lhg6HStjEOrAYLon%2F%2F44JyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=fadfe067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.tvbs.com.tw/amp/ttalk/life/3898</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25e37286c5dd804faacecf16c0da